usdProfileMIB.name: usdProfileMIB

revisions.description: Added ppp(1), pppoe(17) and any(127) to UsdProfileIfEncaps TEXTUAL-CONVENTION.
Added usdProfAssignIfTable, usdProfToIfMapTable to configure and report assignments of profiles to interface/encapsulation pairs.
Initial version of this MIB module.

usdProfileMIB.contactinfo: Unisphere Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 Email: mib@UnisphereNetworks.com
usdProfileMIB.description: The Profile MIB for the Unisphere Networks Inc. enterprise.

UsdProfileIfEncaps.name: UsdProfileIfEncaps
UsdProfileIfEncaps.description: Encapsulated protocol type. The 'any' value is a wildcard value. The DESCRIPTION clause for an object having this syntax must describe how the 'any' value applies, if at all.

usdProfileNameTable.name: usdProfileNameTable
usdProfileNameTable.description: The entries in this table provide mappings of configuration profile names to local integer identifiers for those profiles. These integers are used as indexes into other MIB tables containing profile configuration parameters associated with the same profile name.

usdProfileNameEntry.name: usdProfileNameEntry
usdProfileNameEntry.description: A mapping of a profile name to an integer identifier for that name.

usdProfileNameName.name: usdProfileNameName
usdProfileNameName.description: The profile name uniquely identifying this entry.

usdProfileNameRowStatus.name: usdProfileNameRowStatus
usdProfileNameRowStatus.description: Controls creation/deletion of entries in this table. Only the values 'createAndGo' and 'destroy' may be SET.

usdProfileNameId.name: usdProfileNameId
usdProfileNameId.description: The integer identifier associated with this profile name. This value of this identifier is assigned by the device when an entry in this table is created.

usdProfileIdTable.name: usdProfileIdTable
usdProfileIdTable.description: Provides inverse mapping of profile IDs to profile names.

usdProfileIdEntry.name: usdProfileIdEntry
usdProfileIdEntry.description: A mapping of an integer identifier to a profile name.

usdProfileIdId.name: usdProfileIdId
usdProfileIdId.description: The integer identifier associated with this profile name.

usdProfileIdName.name: usdProfileIdName
usdProfileIdName.description: The profile name having the associated identifier.

usdProfAssignIfTable.name: usdProfAssignIfTable
usdProfAssignIfTable.description: Table providing profile assignment to interface/encapsulation pair. The entries in this table specify which profile to use when creating and configuring a dynamic interface (whose type is identified by the encapsulation) above a specified interface.

usdProfAssignIfEntry.name: usdProfAssignIfEntry
usdProfAssignIfEntry.description: An assignment of a profile to an interface/encapsulation pair.

usdProfAssignIfIndex.name: usdProfAssignIfIndex
usdProfAssignIfIndex.description: The ifIndex of the interface to which the profile is assigned.

usdProfAssignIfEncaps.name: usdProfAssignIfEncaps
usdProfAssignIfEncaps.description: The encapsulated protocol type to which the assigned profile pertains. An interface may have a different profile assigned for each encapsulation it supports. If an entry for a specific encapsulation is absent, the profile assigned for the 'any' encapsulation will be used (if that assignment is present in this table).

usdProfAssignIfRowStatus.name: usdProfAssignIfRowStatus
usdProfAssignIfRowStatus.description: For SET, supports only createAndGo(4) and destroy(6). Returns active(1) when read.

usdProfAssignIfProfileId.name: usdProfAssignIfProfileId
usdProfAssignIfProfileId.description: The ID of the profile assigned to this interface/encapsulation pair.

usdProfToIfMapTable.name: usdProfToIfMapTable
usdProfToIfMapTable.description: Table to report the set of interface/encapsulation pairs assigned to each profile.

usdProfToIfMapEntry.name: usdProfToIfMapEntry
usdProfToIfMapEntry.description: Reports an interface/encapsulation pair assigned to a profile.

usdProfToIfMapProfileId.name: usdProfToIfMapProfileId
usdProfToIfMapProfileId.description: The ID of the profile assigned to this interface/encapsulation pair.

usdProfToIfMapIndex.name: usdProfToIfMapIndex
usdProfToIfMapIndex.description: The ifIndex of the interface to which the profile is assigned.

usdProfToIfMapEncaps.name: usdProfToIfMapEncaps
usdProfToIfMapEncaps.description: The encapsulation type to which the assigned profile pertains. An interface may have a different profile assigned for each encapsulation type it supports.

usdProfileCompliance.name: usdProfileCompliance
usdProfileCompliance.description: Obsolete compliance statement for systems supporting naming of configuration profiles. This statement became obsolete when the interface profile assignment group was added.

usdProfileCompliance2.name: usdProfileCompliance2
usdProfileCompliance2.description: The compliance statement for systems supporting naming of configuration profiles and profile assignment to interfaces.

usdProfileGroup.name: usdProfileGroup
usdProfileGroup.description: The basic collection of objects providing management of Profile naming functionality in a Unisphere product.

usdProfileIfGroup.name: usdProfileIfGroup
usdProfileIfGroup.description: The basic collection of objects providing management of Profile assignment to interfaces in a Unisphere product.
